😿This is one of the worst apps I have ever downloaded because of this app I have lost all of my toenails and shipped my elderly mother to Switzerland 🇨🇭 
Let me tell you
It all started 9 days ago 
My day started out great and normal I had a boiled hotdog✨and hotdog water tea✨for breakfast like I do everyday every morning then I turned my tv on and saw a promotion for this app being the devoted Trump supporter that I am I downloaded it as fast as I could unfortunately it took nearly 8 and a half days to download which I find quite odd considering the fact i only have two other apps and a great deal of data🙀once it was finally done downloading I decided to open it...this is when all hell broke loose as soon as the logo came up I got a text from my credit card company saying I had been hacked and all my money had been stolen and there’s nothing I can do about it 😿then I went back to the app for guidance but a video of my fearless president completely nude popped up he was thanking me for my donation he said “I appreciate your generous donation of your identity” I gasped this was shocking to say the least little did I know this was just the beginning very soon after that Mike Pence jumped through my window landing on my infant child he then proceeded to hollow out a squash with his bare hands and place it over my head after that he tried to brain wash me into believing I was a Swedish foreigner🙀that’s all I remember before falling asleep when I woke I banged my head against one of my doors and cracked the squash till it fell off I then got the sudden urge to call my mother over to my house when she arrived I put her in a refrigerator box 📦 and told her she had 365 days to come back then I sent her off to Switzerland 🇨🇭on the way to the mailbox I dropped the box of my mother onto my toesie woesies😿moral of the story THIS APP IS TERRIBLE AND SHOULD BE TAKEN DOWN
